flowchart TD
    Request[API request] --> Entry{Auth context source}
    Entry -->|Browser via gateway| Headers[X-authentik-* proxy headers]
    Entry -->|External client| OIDC[OIDC bearer token]
    Entry -->|Internal service| Service[Service bearer token]
    Entry -->|Local development| Anonymous[Anonymous local user]
    Headers --> FastAPI[FastAPI auth gate]
    OIDC --> FastAPI
    Service --> FastAPI
    Anonymous --> FastAPI
    FastAPI --> Me[/v1/me identity surface]
    FastAPI --> Method{Unsafe method?}
    Method -->|No| Handler[Route handler]
    Method -->|Yes| RoleCheck{admin / operator / service?}
    RoleCheck -->|Allowed| Handler
    RoleCheck -->|Denied| Forbidden[403 forbidden]
